            <title><![CDATA[金马影帝陈松勇病逝 曾主演《悲情城市》]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-12/8d6fb2d134f22a9a373fc1b07a403a76.jpg?VersionId=Hvs_yX1rQilm2NZfoaBFPrVskQo0HVvV&itok=QVLymqF2" title="以电影《悲情城市》拿下金马奖影帝的演员陈松勇今天病逝。（互联网）" alt="以电影《悲情城市》拿下金马奖影帝的演员陈松勇今天病逝。（互联网）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-12/8d6fb2d134f22a9a373fc1b07a403a76.jpg?VersionId=Hvs_yX1rQilm2NZfoaBFPrVskQo0HVvV&itok=QVLymqF2" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
